column5: Pizza from Il Forno never misses
Chicken was extremely dry and overcooked. Could not be considered edible.
Everyone should try the Bruschetta pizza from Il Forno at least once
Smoothie was basically a frozen chunk of ice. Would not recommend.
Ginger and Soy's bowls are tried and true. WU's most reliable meal
Do not get the falafel. I repeat, do not get the falafel.
